title: Openstreetmap, Baden-wuerttemberg Waterways, Germany, 2008
name: Openstreetmap, Baden-wuerttemberg Waterways, Germany, 2008
description: This data ,provided by openstreetmaps, shows various waterways in the Baden-wuerttemberg administrative area in the country of Germany. Waterways include canals, rivers,streams, and other water bound transportation routes. Data was uploaded as a polygon shape file.
